  "limitations": [
    "This is a checked read-only report contract fixture, not an MCP server, client, runtime, command executor, or report writer.",
    "The sample report is descriptor-only metadata assembled from bounded CLI/core summaries; it does not execute commands or write reports.",
    "No private paths, full logs, generated artifacts, secrets, tokens, provider configuration, model paths, hardware access, or repository mutation are included.",
    "No release, tag, compatibility, hardware, inference, throughput, or timing-closure claim is made."
